he holliday showing\nthe tax reduction program was sure Lo win, and that the soldier bonus\nmeoasure could not be passed over the president's veto,\nAnother construction factor waa Heoretary Mellon's expression of confls\ndence l\u2018\ufb02fl\\rtlluu continued prosperity in 1024, 2\nThe olls and motors featured the fndustrials at the start, Texas Com\npany and Maxwell A reaching now highs on the movement,\nKnowledge of Investment Is\nNecessary, Says Straus\nBY 8. W, STRAUS\nPresident American Soclety for\nThrift\nWhat g thrift? Does it mean\nanything more than just asaving\nmoney?\nRecently an elderly lady in New\nYork lost her lifetime msavings,\namounting to S6OO, which she was\ncurrying in a bag sewed {n her cloth.\ning.\nPostmaster General New made the\nstatement, not long ago, that $1,000,.\n000,000 a year is lost by people of the\nUnited Stateg who purchase fraudu.\nlent securities thruy the mall\u2014an\namount, by the way, equal to two.\nthirds of the estimated total cost of\ngovernment {n the United States, in.\ncluding federal, county, city,. town\nand village expenses,\nThe newspapers froquently tell us\ncases where savings have been\nswept away by carclessness or cu.\npldity.,\nWhat, therefore, did these persons\ngaln by saving thelr money? Would\nthey not have been ns well off had\nthey apent thelr funds as they\nearned them?\nThese questions, which quite nat.\nurally arise in the minds of many,\nare but Indleations of the need of a\nmore genoin! understanding of real\nthrift,\nIt s thrifty to save money, It is\nJust as much a part of thrift to\nknow what to do with 1t after 1t\nhas been saved,\nAnd this fact polnts the way to\none of our greatest public dutiea,\nOur government is dolng every.\nthing it can to encourage the sawv.\nIng of money. Our banks are mak\n\u2018m; stmtlar laudable efforts. In our\nschools, ch'ldren are being taught !n|\nSm\\'n\u2018 School savings banks are\n{growing rapidly all over ths coun.\n*!ry.\nBut not enough is being done and\nsald to bring out the fauct that the\nright care of savings constitutes a\nvital part of thrift practice\nA billlon dollara a year, absolutely\nthrown away, is a heavy penalty mi\u2018\npay for national ignorance in the\nsclence of personal management,\nPublic Markets\nKANITARY\nSialis 243627, 1l bulk eaffes, 3fe;\n8 bars Palmalive soap, 2le: Del Monte\neatsup, 80 pt.; Ghirardelil\u2019s chocolate,\nI\u2122, 200 8 he T9e. Nialle 31-32, lute.\nflake, 16c Alsska smoked salmon, 3%0;\nAlaska King salmon, 28c; freah smelts,\n28\u00a2: genuine scle, 10\u00a2; anchovies In cans,\n{3s\u00a2 and 40e. Hiall 47, Teagarden pre-\nperven, strawberry and raspberry, f3e\nblackberry, 25a 1. marmalads, 232\npure frult Jam or jelly, 20c Htall 157,\nbest butter, S2e 3 Me \u00a71.58; cream\nery butter, 47c, 3 D \u00a71.40; pullet un.l\n31 dox; special choeess, 32\u00a2) oleomars\ngarine, 3 \u2122e 4fe, Htalls R-18-18 Sun\nkist oranges, 20c, 2ie, 30\u00a2; cranberries,\nsoc green peppers, 300; swesl poars,\nfor 35\u00a20; Brussel sprouts. 20e, 3 M\nfhe; grapes, 100 1S aimondas, 20\u00a2 W,\nwalnuts, 30e, 25\u00a2 M.} cocoanuls, 230 e\n25\u00a2; tomatoss, 20c T\ni CORNER\nBralte 192.110, Moyal baking powder,\n38\u00a2; margarine, fresh nut, 2 Me 48e;\nimllod nute, bie) Nlour, 9.1 sack\nSLAS. Htall 2, lamb roast, fec; pork\nroast, 18\u00a2; lamb chops, 2 e 25e; veal\n]rnn.t, 100 sirloln steak, 180; beef steak,\n100, Btalls 16:22, best butller, \u00a7%c, 3\niMa \u00a71.65; creamary butter, 47\u00a2, 3 s\n$1.40; puliet egee, 3l0; ocleomargarine, 32\ne 46c, Hialis \u00a74-96 Plke st short riba,\n\u20ac%el lamb chops, 13%e; mirloln steak,\n16e; olub sausage, 13%\u00a2e; liver, bacon,\n18\u00a2. Htall 14, fresh silver salmon, 206;\nfreah catfish, 26c; skinned acle, 1 e\n38\u00a2; fresh crabs, 2 for 2le.\nPIKE FPLACE\nBiall 17, e bLeal cane sugar, The,\nBtall 81, atorage butler, ke, 2 e, 980;\niYnk!mn honey, \u00a7-1, pall T4e; pullet sxgs,\n{3BO, 3 dox. Tihe; cheese, sharp, 9e\u00a2 .4\